Ispirithalaya is very simple zend project. You can install is very simple way.

    Download Ispirithalaya source.
    Extract to web server.
    Download Zend Framework Full Package. http://framework.zend.com/download/latest
    Add Zend and ZendX libraries to ispirithalaya/library.
    Make database with name ispirithalaya.
    Import database at ispirithalaya/data/db/ispirithalaya.sql (import ispirithalaya-data.sql to sample data)
    Edit database details in ispirithalaya/application/configs/application.ini Change ispirithalaya directory owner to web user.

Enjoy ispirithalaya. 